OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, there
OL,6,Fwill be plenty of dry and bright
OL,7,Fweather around on Sunday. Skies may
OL,8,Fturn a little hazy into the afternoon.
OL,9,FLight winds and temperatures below
OL,10,Faverage for early to mid-May.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright start to the
OL,13,Fevening, however cloud will build from
OL,14,Fthe north with showery outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain reaching the region during the
OL,16,Fsecond half of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
